## Layout Structure
```
header (full width)
weather bar (full width)
main (max-width: 1800px, centered, margin: 0 auto)
  └── .mgrid (320px | 1fr | 320px, width: 100%)
        ├── [grid-column: 1/-1] KPI strip (6 cards)
        ├── LEFT col (320px): Quick Launch, Content Creation, Business Bills
        ├── CENTER col (1fr, min-width:0): Business Pulse, Calendar, Smart Notes, Lead Pipeline
        └── RIGHT col (320px): Task Manager, Meetings, Local Map
```

---

## Key JavaScript Functions
| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `connectGoogle()` | Initiates Google OAuth implicit flow |
| `onOAuthConnected()` | Called after successful OAuth, starts all Google syncs |
| `fetchOAuthCalendar()` | Fetches all calendar events from all user calendars |
| `fetchGoogleTasks()` | Fetches tasks from Google Tasks API |
| `fetchHLData()` | Syncs leads from HighLevel pipeline |
| `renderKanban()` | Renders lead pipeline board |
| `processNote()` | Sends note to Claude via proxy, extracts tasks |
| `loadNoteHistory()` | Loads Smart Notes from Google Sheets |
| `archiveNote(sheetRow, btn)` | Moves note to Archived Notes tab |
| `autoArchiveDoneRows(doneRows)` | Batch archives Done notes |
| `fetchJobberMetrics()` | Reads Dashboard!B2:G2 from Job Tracker sheet |
| `fetchSheetKPIs()` | Reads KPI values from Job Tracker sheet |
| `refreshAll()` | Calls all fetch functions |
| `renderCalendar()` | Renders the calendar grid |
| `mobNav(id)` | Switches mobile section |
| `toggleDeadCol()` | Shows/hides Dead Lead column (persisted) |
| `toggleWonCol()` | Shows/hides Job Completed column (persisted) |
| `mobAppLink(e, appUrl, webUrl)` | Opens native app on mobile, web URL on desktop |

---

## Smart Notes System
- New notes default to status: **"Needs Processing"**
- Status dropdown: `Needs Processing / In Progress / Done / Archived`
- When History panel opens: auto-archives any rows with status "Done" or "Archived"
- **Apps Script trigger** (`SmartNotes_AutoArchive.gs`): installed in Google Sheet, fires on edit — when Status col (I) → "Done", instantly moves row to Archived Notes tab and deletes from Smart Notes
- `SN_SHEET_ID = JOB_TRACKER_SHEET_ID` (same sheet)

---

## Mobile / PWA
- Bottom nav bar with 5 tabs: Overview, Tasks, Calendar, Notes, More
- Nav buttons use class `.mnb`, IDs `mnb-home`, `mnb-tasks`, `mnb-notes`, `mnb-pipeline`, `mnb-more`
- Section IDs: `mob-home-section`, `mob-tasks-section`, `mob-notes-section`, `mob-pipeline-section`, `mob-more-section`
- `mobNav(id)` — the main nav function
- Mobile breakpoint: 900px (`.mob-section{display:none}` only at ≤900px)
- PWA installable via manifest.json + sw.js
- Native app deep links via `mobAppLink()` helper

---

## Important Coding Conventions
1. **Single file** — everything stays in `CHS_Dashboard.html`, no separate CSS/JS files
2. **No `_orig*` override patterns** — causes infinite recursion due to JS hoisting. Always merge new logic directly into the original function
3. **Null-safe DOM access** — always check `if(!el)return` before accessing element properties
4. **localStorage keys in use**:
   - `chs_oauth` — OAuth token + expiry
   - `chs_leads_kb` — kanban leads array
   - `chs_dead_hidden` — dead col hidden state
   - `chs_won_hidden` — won col hidden state
   - `chs_kb_ver` — version key to reset stale hide states
   - `chs_mob_sec` — last active mobile section
   - `chs_tr1`, `chs_tr2` — spreadsheet URLs
   - `chs_trl1`, `chs_trl2` — spreadsheet lock states
   - `chs_sub` — subcontractor sheet URL
   - `chs_sub_locked` — sub sheet lock state
5. **Calendar all-day events** — Google returns date-only strings like `"2026-04-07"`. Parse with string splitting, NOT `new Date("2026-04-07")` (which shifts timezone to previous day in US time zones)
6. **Syntax checking** — always run `node --check` on the extracted script before deploying

